name: MYTHIC
description: Barong or also called Barongan is one of the Indonesian mythological creatures originating from the culture of the Javanese and Balinese people. In Javanese and Balinese mythology and legends, Barong is a symbol of the values ​​of goodness and justice. He leads the good forces in the battle against the evil forces led by a demon named Rangda in the form of an ugly old woman.
